      <title>Availability of supporting data</title>
      <p>The source code for AsmVar is available at <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://github.com/bioinformatics-centre/AsmVar">https://github.com/bioinformatics-centre/AsmVar</ext-link>. Example data and snapshots of the code are also available in the <italic>GigaScience</italic> GigaDB database [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR26">26</xref>].</p>
